Package: ggdirect
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: DRM/KMS rendering backend for GGUI applications
 GGDirect provides the DRM/KMS-based rendering backend used by
 GGUI terminal applications. It handles framebuffer setup, input
 multiplexing, and direct rendering for TUI environments that
 require low-level display access without a windowing system.
